88
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,970
Bai Yue!

89
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,119
Bai Yue!

90
00:11:01,659 --> 00:11:03,559
Bai Yue!

91
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:05,533
Bai Yue, are you all right?

92
00:11:06,659 --> 00:11:09,900
Uncle Hui. Why are you here?

93
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:12,100
Did you see a woman in red just now?

94
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:13,559
Where is a woman in red?

95
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:15,859
