103
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,659
You were seriously hurt this time.

104
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:45,120
Here.

105
00:13:48,939 --> 00:13:51,000
Your speed of recovery is quite fast.

106
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,485
But you still need to recuperate well.

107
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:57,559
Has someone been in here?

108
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,120
Probably the medicine boy.

109
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,200
You've eaten the ginseng.

110
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,639
Drink the ginseng broth, too.

111
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:11,200
This was the last ginseng.

112
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:15,019
In the entire Changliu Mountain, there is no more to be found.

113
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:27,360
All right. Rest and recuperate well.

114
00:14:28,559 --> 00:14:30,359
Wait, Uncle Hui.

115
00:14:31,799 --> 00:14:35,199
Just now, there was someone dressed in red.

116
00:14:35,199 --> 00:14:37,459
You must be wrong. There's no one dressed in red here.

117
00:14:37,459 --> 00:14:39,020
It's true.

118
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:40,480
She was also in the underground palace.

119
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,960
That's impossible. Who else can come in here?

120
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:45,759
Ever since you got into trouble, it's been strictly guarded.

121
00:14:45,759 --> 00:14:47,240
The underground palace is already closed.

122
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:52,300
You rascal. If you barge into the forbidden area again, I'll really have to punish you harshly.

123
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:54,519
That's enough. Get a good rest.

124
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:45,639
Who's there?

125
00:15:45,639 --> 00:15:47,239
Come out!

126
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:53,620
You are the girl in the underground palace?

127
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:54,840
Who are you?

128
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:58,000
My name is Ye Xi, a little ginseng fairy.

129
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,180
I'll help you.

130
00:16:16,879 --> 00:16:20,939
Bai Yue, you are so kindhearted.

131
00:16:20,939 --> 00:16:22,900
Thank you for saving me.

132
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:24,080
Sleep.

133
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,479
Get a good sleep.

134
00:16:25,479 --> 00:16:27,959
Everything will be fine when you wake up.

135
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:38,240
Is it necessary to re-arrange the mechanisms?

136
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,679
It's quite a hassle.

137
00:16:39,679 --> 00:16:41,600
Such a big incident occurred in the underground palace.

138
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:44,019
It's necessary to review the precautions.

139
00:16:44,019 --> 00:16:47,719
Ever since Bai Yue got hurt last time, he's been in a daze.

140
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:49,080
He doesn't remember who happened.

141
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:50,559
He's even had hallucinations.

142
00:16:50,559 --> 00:16:52,940
He said there are strangers in the valley.

143
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,399
That would be hallucinations.

144
00:16:54,399 --> 00:16:57,800
Our Fenghua Valley is impenetrable.

145
00:16:57,800 --> 00:17:00,159
Better safe than sorry.

146
00:17:00,159 --> 00:17:01,480
Let's get to work. No more complaining.

147
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,280
Sure. Let's go.

148
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,279
Don't worry.

149
00:17:18,279 --> 00:17:20,699
He will be fine very soon.

150
00:17:23,799 --> 00:17:26,519
But it's really exhausting.

151
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:29,159
I need to go back to sleep.

152
00:17:33,619 --> 00:17:37,310
Maybe I have to wait until my hair grows long again to recover.

153
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:42,400
At that time, I'll have to cultivate some more before I can return to visit you.

154
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:53,130
[Six Months Later]

155
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:59,959
Congratulations, Valley Master, to have fully recovered.

156
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,939
I have news about the girl you asked me to inquire about.

157
00:18:03,939 --> 00:18:05,939
Her name is Ye Xi.

158
00:18:05,939 --> 00:18:08,140
She was cheated by Tang Yang, Young Lord of the Tang Sect,

159
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:10,419
into believing the Storm Pear Flower Needle belonged to the Tang Sect

160
00:18:10,419 --> 00:18:12,600
and that it was taken by the Mo Sect.

161
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:16,759
So she helped Tang Yang to retrieve the Storm Pear Flower Needle.

162
00:18:30,420 --> 00:18:33,200
[Mo Sect]

163
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:36,499
But Tang Yang claimed he was avenging the Mo Sect

164
00:18:36,499 --> 00:18:40,219
but actually used the opportunity to annihilate the Mo Sect.

165
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:53,220
Tang Yang also cajoled the lone survivor, Mo family's eldest miss, Mo Rou,

166
00:18:53,220 --> 00:18:56,060
to testify against Ye Xi and caused outrage in the martial arts world.

167
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:59,300
Right now, all the major sects are pursuing Ye Xi.

168
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:11,320
- Don't run!
- Stop right there!

169
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:13,059
Stop right there!

170
00:19:14,319 --> 00:19:16,100
Stop right there! Stop right there!

171
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:17,419
Stop right there!

172
00:19:17,419 --> 00:19:19,319
Don't run!

173
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,400
Demoness!

174
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:33,699
Hand over the Storm Pear Flower Needle!

175
00:19:33,699 --> 00:19:36,200
It's up to you to believe it or not,

176
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:39,350
but Tang Sect's trouble has nothing to do with me.

177
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:42,900
The eldest miss of Mo Sect testified to the Lord of Martial Arts World Alliance

178
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:47,319
that you are the culprit who stole the Storm Pear Flower Needle and killed everyone in the Mo Sect.

179
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:51,240
Tang Sect also testified that you unsuccessfully seduced Young Lord Tang Yang,

180
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:54,000
and then stole the secret books from the Tang Sect and the other sects.

181
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:56,340
A demoness like you who does all kinds of evil,

182
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:59,400
we must uphold justice for everyone in the martial arts world.

183
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,839
Brothers, kill this demoness!

184
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:03,680
Let's eradicate evil for the martial arts world.

185
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:05,760
I've never killed anyone.

186
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:08,400
Is justice in the martial arts world

187
00:20:09,119 --> 00:20:12,200
so indiscriminate?

188
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,040
Come at me then!

189
00:20:48,179 --> 00:20:53,840
Heaven as my witness, not killing is harder than killing.

190
00:20:53,840 --> 00:20:56,359
It's been so hard for me.

191
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:41,279
Xiao Xi, I'm here to pick you up.

192
00:21:41,279 --> 00:21:43,240
Come home with me.

193
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:48,880
You're also here to kill me.

194
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:53,560
Xiao Xi, you always surprise me.

195
00:21:54,339 --> 00:21:56,960
Your martial arts are outstanding.

196
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:59,900
I'm sure not many in the martial arts world are a match for you.

197
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:01,939
So what?

198
00:22:04,459 --> 00:22:08,099
Must I be the public enemy of the whole martial arts world?

199
00:22:08,099 --> 00:22:10,980
You're to blame for this.

200
00:22:10,980 --> 00:22:13,219
They accuse me of seducing you.

201
00:22:13,219 --> 00:22:15,699
When have I ever done that?

202
00:22:15,699 --> 00:22:18,259
Weren't you the one who adored my chivalrous nature?

203
00:22:18,259 --> 00:22:20,800
I was fooled into believing that you were a righteous man.

204
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:22,739
Xiao Xi,

205
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:26,660
I genuinely adore you.

206
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:29,979
You possess an ethereal beauty and phenomenal martial arts.

207
00:22:29,979 --> 00:22:36,199
However, I married Mo Rou because Mo Sect has the Storm Pear Flower Needle that I desire.

208
00:22:36,199 --> 00:22:38,299
Yet, they still treated me like a stranger.

209
00:22:38,299 --> 00:22:42,220
In that case, they're forcing me and Tang Sect to resort to extreme measures.

210
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:45,780
How am I involved in your scuffles?

211
00:22:52,260 --> 00:22:54,319
I don't wish to hurt you either.

212
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:58,840
Let us reunite in our next lives.

213
00:23:20,179 --> 00:23:24,219
The needle is tipped with Tang Sect's new Tears of Yearning concoction.

214
00:23:24,219 --> 00:23:26,859
In fact, as simple word like love

215
00:23:27,839 --> 00:23:30,559
is the most lethal poison.

216
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:38,419
At least bury me.

217
00:23:38,419 --> 00:23:41,599
I didn't want to kill you either,

218
00:23:42,519 --> 00:23:46,320
but Mo Rou brings more benefits than you do.

219
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:48,100
She has what I want.

220
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:50,839
I can only trade for it with your life.

221
00:23:50,839 --> 00:23:54,419
It's not easy for me to serve Tang Sect either.

222
00:23:56,219 --> 00:23:58,600
Don't resent me for this.

223
00:24:00,499 --> 00:24:04,470
In this life, we can only part.

224
00:24:05,090 --> 00:24:07,319
Farewell.

225
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:17,480
Ye Xi.

226
00:25:18,260 --> 00:25:21,920
The moment I heard about you, I dashed over from the mountains.

227
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,739
I was still too late.

228
00:25:26,559 --> 00:25:29,999
I know you're the girl who saved me in the ancient tomb.

229
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:35,520
I didn't think that parting would be an eternal farewell.

230
00:25:37,019 --> 00:25:40,060
I can no longer repay my debt of gratitude.

231
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:45,319
Martial artists boast about their chivalry,

232
00:25:45,319 --> 00:25:50,300
but those who can truly sacrifice themselves for others are few and far between.

233
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:57,700
Yet, someone as kind as you has been sullied by the world.

234
00:25:57,700 --> 00:26:00,460
They even caused your ruin.

235
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:05,639
Thank goodness you're a ginseng fairy.

236
00:26:05,639 --> 00:26:08,440
Ginseng grows in the ground.

237
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:11,280
I've checked the ancient records.

238
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:13,659
I'll bury you deep in the ground.

239
00:26:13,659 --> 00:26:16,559
May you reawaken one day.

240
00:26:17,519 --> 00:26:22,319
There's a chance that your memory will be wiped clean.

241
00:26:23,739 --> 00:26:26,300
However, as long as you open those eyes again,

242
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:30,080
I will find you .

243
00:26:34,950 --> 00:26:45,260
♫ I will wait for you for the rest of my life ♫

244
00:26:48,020 --> 00:26:51,450
